result.name: After Taste Coffee

reviews.text:
Nice decor inside but the food was very average considering the price. The baked beans were stone cold. The female server was quite rude in her presence, a smile wouldn't go amiss! They also didn't accept cash which we only found out when we came to pay so I had to walk in the rain to get cash.

It took around 30-35 minutes to cook which is a very lengthy time.

Newly opened (for about a month) coffee shop at SYP — Cute quaint shop right on the slope.

Pleasant experience with Tony the barista — he’s welcome to share his coffee experience.

🥑x 🥚x 🥐 x ☕️ 
We ordered {Avocado & eggs}
- Choice of eggs : scrambled/over easy)
- Choice of bread : toast / croissant 

Latte @HK$42 — nice latte art. I got a choice between nutty / fruity beans - I opted for nutty {Indonesian beans} First experience with a choice of beans for latte~ nice ! 👍🏻

Pour over @HK$70 — {Costa Rica • roasted at Taiwan}
You can smell the winey 🍷 aroma but it wasn’t tart at all. The sake cups was a great size. Not too big allows coffee to cool down and it’s easier to drink. 

Overall experience was great. 
Would gladly come back. 👏🏻 ☕️💕
Ok

2019.05.24

聖母@After Taste Coffee

哥斯大黎加
蜜處理
Roast by Tamp Temper Taichung Coffee

“有什麼特別的豆？”
咖啡師 Tony 拎出豆來排陣。
“這支酒味濃。”

風味有葡萄、紅酒、香草。

乾粉味淡，聞不出什麼來。

沖好，一聞，嗯，真的有酒香。
不是酒發酵的味，
是開瓶後酒香四溢那種。

溫度越低酒味越濃，
後段加入葡萄清酸。

“這支從台中少量買入，
Seasonal，下期應該沒有。”

Backyard ，高樓包圍小天地，

reviews.text: Friendly service but the worst pizza i ve had in hong kong and one of the worst pizza experience ever. We ordered a margharita and a pepperoni pizza for delivery -~ ard 326hkd. Dough not fresh, oily base, no tomato taste, cheese felt like cardboard. I called the store to qualify the experience as the “most disgusting pizza in hong kong”. Go to Alfy s instead.
Good quality pizza with reasonable price. Operated by some nice Indian guys.
It was a nice place,I enjoy to watch the view

I was hoping for more when I saw the star rating of this place but this did not at all reflect the food. The base of the pizza was not fresh, it was used from a packet, the pizza was extremely oily, neo sauce was average, and we both felt guilty after eating it. Price was reasonable but I would not suggest coming here if you want good pizza.

This place is full of false reviews. Note the picture posted from the owner is a WOODFIRED pizza but they only have a standard oven. FALSE advertising!
